title: Vyšehrad
overview: Julius "Lavi" Lavický was a great football talent. However, parties, alcohol, smoking, girls and the escapade behind the escapade ruin his promising career. He doesn't even play for Sparta, from which he left in style, but "only" for Vyšehrad. Will he be chopping Latin at this family club, run by a charismatic owner, or are there even more mythical stories waiting for us? Series from own OBBOD production.
